blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[Overhear PSRR PPDU] --> B{Identified as inter-BSS?}
  B -- no --> X[No PSR opportunity]
  B -- yes --> C{PSRT PPDU queued and<br/>power budget met?}
  C -- no --> X
  C -- yes --> D[Transmit PSRT PPDU<br/>at reduced power]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[听到 PSRR PPDU] --> B{识别为 BSS 间?}
  B -- 否 --> X[无 PSR 机会]
  B -- 是 --> C{已排队 PSRT PPDU 且<br/>满足功率预算?}
  C -- 否 --> X
  C -- 是 --> D[以降低功率<br/>发送 PSRT PPDU]
